# PLC DEBUG FULL ADVANCED PATCH
# Adds: live table colors, pause/freeze monitor, search/filter,
# bit view, register trend, force timeout, alarm banner,
# protected addresses, favorites, scaling note, comm statistics,
# improved error decode, dashboard counters, and audit export.
# This patch keeps the original PLC Debug logic and only extends it.
